{
  "name": "Gmail AI Auto-Reply Agent",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Gmail Trigger\nPolls Gmail every minute for new UNREAD emails and returns the full message (sender, subject, body) for analysis.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300
      },
      "id": "00f67700-a795-4c82-8a0e-39a8a15e8311",
      "name": "Sticky Note 00f67700",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        -48
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2-3. AI Email Assistant\nReads sender, subject and body, classifies the email (genuine / promotional / spam / newsletter) and drafts a polite, concise, professional reply. Uses OpenAI GPT + a structured output parser.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300
      },
      "id": "52cc3bcd-40b6-479b-bbd0-c9780ba31b4a",
      "name": "Sticky Note 52cc3bcd",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        -48
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 4-5. Should Reply?\nOnly genuine emails continue. Promotional, spam and newsletter emails hit the false branch and are ignored (no reply).",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300
      },
      "id": "a4fc5ae4-930f-45ba-a9d5-06ada6d0548d",
      "name": "Sticky Note a4fc5ae4",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        -48
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 7-8. Reply & Mark as Read\nSends the generated reply to the sender in the original thread, then marks the original email as read.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300
      },
      "id": "21b2c405-b613-4c9b-ae80-a5cf668ed7d2",
      "name": "Sticky Note 21b2c405",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        -48
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "pollTimes": {
          "item": [
            {
              "mode": "everyMinute"
            }
          ]
        },
        "simple": false,
        "filters": {
          "readStatus": "unread"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "8a540881-c391-484f-9f26-980f87f5955d",
      "name": "Gmail Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmailTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.4,
